dct_title_s: The forty yeares travels of children of Israel out of Egypt through the Red Sea, and ye wilderne√ü into Canaan or the land of promise
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Bar scale on map given in "English miles".
Illustrations of a fish, ships, and settlements throughout.
Shows topography, drainage, territorial boundaries of the tribes of Israel, travel routes (with numbered sites), places of historical interest.
Includes key: This is the mark of the six cities of refuge.
Descriptive text throughout, e.g.: The prophet Jonas being cast into the sea is swallowed by a fish...
